{"article_id":"zz2jO1MoG0Jhfu5w","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump declared as \" dead \" on Monday a program","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"that protects immigrants","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"brought to the United States illegally as children","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"and pressed Congress to pass legislation","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"to secure the U.S. border with Mexico .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Trump ' s latest comments on immigration ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"made via Twitter ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"came as the U.S. Department of Justice moved to establish first-ever quotas for immigration judges","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"aimed at speeding up cases","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"and clearing a backlog .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Trump said in September","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"he would terminate the Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals","depth":13},{"id":13,"text":"( DACA )","depth":13},{"id":14,"text":"program","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"introduced by his Democratic predecessor , Barack Obama ,","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"but gave the Republican-controlled Congress until March 6","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"to replace it .","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"Congress failed to meet that deadline ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"but courts have ruled","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"the program can stay in place for now .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"\" DACA is dead","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"because the Democrats didn ' t care or act ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"and now everyone wants to get onto the DACA bandwagon , \"","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"the Republican president said in a Twitter post .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Trump also urged Congress to \" pass tough laws","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"and build the WALL , \"","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"referring to a U.S.-Mexico border wall","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"he has championed as a way","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"to curb illegal immigration and the flow of drugs .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"In a move","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"aimed at speeding deportations ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"the Department of Justice sent an email on Friday to federal immigration judges","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"telling them","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"their job performance would be evaluated","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"based on how quickly they close cases .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Judges will be required to complete at least 700 cases a year and have fewer than 15 percent of their decisions appealed and remanded back ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"according to Dana Marks , spokeswoman for the National Association of Immigration Judges .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Another metric demands","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"that 85 percent of removal cases for detained immigrants be completed within three days of a hearing on the merits of the case .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"The new policy is expected to take effect on Oct. 1 .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"A growing backlog of immigration cases reached 687,000 in March ,","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"according to a analysis of court records ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"and caused asylum seekers to wait years","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"to present their cases .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Amiena Khan , executive vice president of the immigration judges ' union , said","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"the new rules threatened to interfere with judicial independence .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"\" It ' s going to create havoc within the courts , \"","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"said Khan ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"who also serves as an immigration judge in New York .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"\" The integrity of the entire process is at risk . \"","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"On Monday , senior administration officials told reporters","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"that legislation was being prepared","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"aimed at helping speed deportations of some illegal immigrants .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"They did not provide a timetable","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"for submitting it to Congress","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"and did not say","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"whether provisions","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"to help DACA recipients","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"would be included .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"No immigration deal has materialized in the Republican-controlled Congress","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"despite months of efforts .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"The Senate considered several immigration proposals in February","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"but rejected all of them ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"including bipartisan bills and legislation","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"tailored to Trump ' s requirements .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Democrats have blamed Trump for the tenuous status of the DACA program","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"that shielded hundreds of thousands of young immigrants ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"often called \" Dreamers , \"","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"from deportation","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"and gave them work permits .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Dick Durbin , the No . 2 Senate Democrat , said in a telephone interview :","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"\" After the experience","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"of giving this president six different bipartisan options","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"and having him reject them all ...","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"I don ' t believe","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"we have a reliable partner \" in negotiations","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"that are now dormant .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"In the past , Trump had said","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"he was open to a deal with congressional Democrats","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"in which they would support funding for the border wall in exchange for protection for the Dreamers .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"But on Sunday , he indicated","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"that the time had passed ,","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"writing on Twitter :","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"\" ' Caravans ' coming .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"Republicans must go to Nuclear Option","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"to pass tough laws NOW .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"NO MORE DACA DEAL ! \"","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump waves to the media","depth":5},{"id":89,"text":"as he arrives with first lady Melania Trump at Joint Base Andrews in Maryland , U.S. , after the Easter weekend in Palm Beach , Florida , April 1 , 2018 .","depth":5},{"id":90,"text":"/Yuri Gripas","depth":4},{"id":91,"text":"The mention of a caravan apparently referred to a group of 1,500 men , women and children from Honduras , Guatemala and El Salvador","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"who are traveling in a \" refugee caravan \"","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"organized by the U.S.-based immigration advocacy group Pueblo sin Fronteras ,","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"whose Spanish name means People Without Borders .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"By traveling together ,","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"the immigrants hope to protect themselves from the crime and extortion","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"that makes the route through Mexico toward the U.S. border dangerous .","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"They say","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"some but not all of them will seek asylum","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"if they reach the United States .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"\" The only person","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"gaming DACA","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"is not in the caravan .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"He ' s in the Oval Office \" of the White House ,","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"Durbin said ,","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"referring to Trump .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":213,"left":0,"right":212,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":212,"left":193,"right":211,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":